# 1️⃣ Create API Service Layer (Important)

Create a folder:

```
src/api
```

Create file:

```
chatApi.ts
```

Example API function:

```ts
export const sendMessage = async (message: string): Promise<string> => {

  // simulate API delay
  return new Promise((resolve) => {
    setTimeout(() => {
      resolve(`AI reply to: ${message}`)
    }, 1200)
  })

}
```

This **simulates a real backend**.

